        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/petko147/{size}/42282_2.png",
        "created_at": "2023-07-20T13:41:52.429Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hi, I have a lot of old groups I don‚Äôt use anymore, and I want to leave them, because some of those group names even compromise my privacy. Most of those groups were used for like 1 time event, and is not meant to be used long term. I see those groups when I tap on some friend and I see all the groups we have in common.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>But there is no place I can see all the groups I am in</li>\n<li>It is not possible to leave these groups silently, so I will spam each friend in each group I want to leave with the notification that I left. It would be awesome, if I could leave the group silently, so nobody get‚Äôs notified.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>I would greatly appreciate these 2 features <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"><br>\nAnyway, you are doing a fantastic job with Signal, I really love this app and I will continue to donate few euros each month <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>Have a great day <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
