        "created_at": "2023-07-20T14:30:59.396Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I would think that there needs to be some notification so that other group members don‚Äôt assume that you are still in the group. I haven‚Äôt left nor had someone leave a group in which I am a member, so I don‚Äôt know what actually occurs. Is it an operating system notification or simply a message within the group chat? I message in the group chat is not too burdensome.</p>",
