        "created_at": "2023-07-20T20:00:42.620Z",
        "cooked": "<p>nice thanks I didn‚Äôt know that, I just looked at some ancient group, so I thought it is still V1 <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/smiley.png?v=12\" title=\":smiley:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":smiley:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"><br>\nIt shows the message, so when you had the group already deleted, it will be shown again‚Ä¶  Which spams your inbox, you have some older groups shows again even when you deleted them long time ago‚Ä¶</p>\n<p>If there is some chance of introducing this feature, I would be super happy.<br>\nAnd of course the feature in which you can delete the group for everybody.</p>\n<p>Those are privacy oriented features, so pretty well desired in Signal <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
